<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; padding: 20px; }
      .button { background-color: #007bff; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius:
      4px; text-decoration: none; color: white; display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
    <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>
    <p>You recently requested to reset your password. Click the button below to
      reset it:</p>
    <a class="button" href="{{resetPasswordLink}}">Reset Password</a>
    <p>If you did not request this, you can ignore this email.</p>
    <p>This link will expire in 15 minutes.</p>
    <br />
    <p>Thanks,<br />The Bubblify Team</p>
  </body>
</html>